(:-
 :
 : This XQuery module display XML interlinear glossed texts in EMELD XML 
 : format and associated dictionary in LIFT XML format.
 :
 : Public domain
 : Sylvain Loiseau
 : <sylvain.loiseau@univ-paris13.fr>
